  <brief_title>Drug Related Problems Among Patients With Femoral Neck Fractures in an Orthopedic Ward</brief_title>
  <official_title>Identification and Characterization of Drug Related Problems Among Patients With Femoral Neck Fractures in an Orthopedic Ward</official_title>
