  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the purpose of the study is to:

        1. Identify and characterize drug related problems in patients after a femur neck fracture
           that are hospitalized in the orthopedic department at &quot;Meir&quot; medical center.

        2. Evaluate the contribution of a clinical pharmacist in identifying,characterizing and
           preventing drug related problems in patients after a femur neck fracture that are
           hospitalized in the orthopedic department at &quot;Meir&quot; medical center.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
